        <mxCell id="notesBox" value="Notes&lt;br&gt;• HCP model: Staging/Prod control planes (kube-apiserver, etcd, OAuth, Ignition, Konnectivity) run as pods on the Infra cluster — workers reach them over the blue paths.&lt;br&gt;• Pure Storage over NFS: TCP/2049 (NFSv4). rpcbind TCP+UDP/111 only needed if NFSv3 is in play — drop it if we mount v4.1 only.&lt;br&gt;• etcd 2379-2380, kube-controller-manager 10257, kube-scheduler 10259 apply only within the Infra cluster (standalone control plane) and inside HCP pod networks — not worker VLANs." style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;dashed=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;fontSize=11;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;spacing=8;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="-245" y="270" width="320" height="330" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
